{"type": "article", "id": 48556, "title": "混凝土做成的水果托盘，也是个艺术装饰品｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-12-24T23:18:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 46522, "name": "LOEWE"}, {"id": 46523, "name": "New Duivendrecht"}, {"id": 46524, "name": "Redemption Roasters"}, {"id": 46525, "name": "Here Design"}, {"id": 46526, "name": "STUDIO LEE SANGHYEOK"}, {"id": 46527, "name": "Aljoud Lootah"}, {"id": 33069, "name": "Fabio Vogel"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171224215533OHgSaQGv3yf25iFI.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Bild X Concept TV by LOEWE</h3><p>今年的柏林国际电子消费品及家电展览会上，德国品牌 LOEWE 提出了一款概念产品 Bild X Concept TV，拿到了权威设计杂志 Wallpaper* 设计奖的提名，称其把电视设计带到了一个新的方向。</p><p>伦敦设计师 Bodo Sperlein 为其创造了一个薄薄的金色框架，灵感来自帆船上风帆的悬挂方式，突出其超薄 OLED 屏幕的特点，他将轻薄的屏幕与美学相结合，创造出具备收藏价值的电视艺术品，同时为日常生活提供更多的娱乐选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215605XGgP2smjeST1pl0n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215605ANBXqZGF17hQbRM2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215605wJ7xfiQ4aqjYHZeb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017122421560678na3EwISkOoUsfJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215606FECHjtSDhTwUcKpM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>“Arch” trays by New Duivendrecht</h3><p>把托盘当成艺术装饰品来做，这是荷兰设计工作室 New Duivendrecht 创作 Arch 托盘的思路。厚实的混凝土被塑造为微微的拱形结构，创造了一个平衡的微空间。设计师也很注意色调的搭配，安静的米色搭配充满活力的猩红色色调，营造出一种微妙的拼图感觉。售价 40.50 至 48.76 欧元，<a href=\"http://newduivendrecht.com/shop/arch/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215646V5tD6wYOUkx9Ipli.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612798\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215646wJaDhTeBFGnoc4iM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215646bsVOteK2ERCThxg1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215646CEaiWevn9YIT6GlR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215646CVyloas3enZ6x9rW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215646hL6e2bpnswMY1A8G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The latest furniture collection by Aljoud Lootah</h3><p>Alareesh 结构是一种传统的阿联酋建筑形式，由干枯的棕榈叶建造而成，经过垂直摆放并用绳子将其连接起来。这些简单的围墙就像是人们的庇护所，让他们远离列日、狂风与沙尘。然而，因其特殊的结构，这些嵌板实现保护功能的同时还提供通风。</p><p>迪拜设计师 Aljoud Lootah 以此为灵感设计的“alareesh”系列，采用了传统建筑形状，利用玫瑰金材料，在光影之间实现一种有趣的交互，根据不同的视角与背景而产生相应的变化。传统建筑的构建方式经过缩小尺寸后变成了一系列家具作品，包括房间隔断、咖啡桌、凳子与台灯等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215711PJrYRSj3y8FMW7sf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.977995\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215711QH1YSaeuBArCEyFh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215711mqQTHJsNhy18AIMY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215711q6X8KE1Q0ihcRmwr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215712FbhqE5sHucy392lv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>New Brand Identity for Redemption Roasters by Here Design</h3><p>伦敦设计工作室 Here Design 为咖啡品牌 Redemption Roasters 设计了全新品牌形象。Redemption Roasters 内部设有烘焙工坊和咖啡学院，向当地的咖啡馆、批发商和消费者提供新鲜烘焙的咖啡豆。特别的是，这家公司雇佣的员工多是艾尔斯伯里的青少年拘留所的少年犯。</p><p>为了突出这一特征，设计师将品牌名称中的两个 R 结合在一起，形成了一个钥匙孔，一是代表打开了监狱之门，二是代表挖掘青少年尚未被挖掘的潜力。同时使用多种颜色和符号，试图讲述烘焙咖啡豆的故事，吸引更广泛的消费者。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215738gQ1r7W9NjEwJMPm3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215738szTyuQBZLxvJ6HoD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215738cDi0RyZJvA6xftCO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215739SX8KIbjy921A4sdg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215738LX83sF5UYjqCoiPS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215739Misxf2yWKJBw79Zt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>I'll be your mirror by STUDIO LEE SANGHYEOK</h3><p>这是韩国设计工作室 STUDIO LEE SANGHYEOK 推出的一款创意家居作品，由两片弯曲的不锈钢钢板组合而成，可以转换出五种不同形式的镜子。</p><p>由于两片钢板的独立关系，设计师为观者提供了多样的视觉感受。这个项目的表现形式更像是家中的一件雕塑作品，但同时又兼具镜子微妙和简单的功能。售价 185 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.analograum.com/raum/ill-be-your-mirror\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712242158587c6l0hmv1esIaYVg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666471\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215858FTJjYkiOoP5rIHld.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215858aUHKCGknBgMEdj9h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215858Ke3dEaujqG4x1Azm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215859qCRYJBbVNWZ4x8pT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215858ZnpQHklE0GaAImy4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>105 ltr formen by Fabio Vogel</h3><p>来自于德国的青年设计师 Fabio Vogel 设计了一套名为 105 ltr formen 的新款系列花瓶，该套多功能花瓶采用了玻璃外壳，将各种方法技艺相结合，利用防火布料对最终的形状进行塑造与影响。</p><p>设计师围绕火这一元素进行创作，手工吹制而成的玻璃，将火的破坏力与创造力两种对比鲜明的力量关系结合在一起。花瓶由防火布料模具塑造而成，可以清楚地看到花瓶表面的压痕与缝线，有一种将玻璃光滑优雅的美感与织物的传统与磨损效果结合在一起的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215933sphu0AWU2CwTjLoI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215933eBrPq8Z09SN4Ol2c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215933PHU12bVBYCw4hK7g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215933LKX7H51g4CtTrmPM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.461458\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215933QvzBUPR2Hce8uifw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171224215933gWUYPqcDdsu6xV4Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}